  "wd.hat_helmet": "Now that the hat is stained with glowing jam, the magician can safely stay in the cave, because the light of the jam blinds the local inhabitants, which is why they consider the owner almost a god... but hostile or peaceful, it is up to the wizard to decide directly. It is worth noting that it has become catchy in the eyes of travelers, so it is better not to attract their attention.",
  "wd.hat_helmet_clear": "The look of the owner of such a hat becomes modest, from which the travelers of the end calmly tolerate the company of the owner of the hat.",
  "wd.healing_dew": "The strongest medicine that can cure an infected resident...in most cases.",
  "wd.nether_grog": "Cherished by all — elemants and piglins alike. Offer this to a piglin, and it will remain friendly, even under the sunlight after leaving the portal.",
